</p>
<p>A/HRC/26/21, NGA 1/2014, UGA 1/2014, UGA 1/2013; A/HRC/27/72, KGZ/1/2014.  
</p>
<p> 80 A/HRC/25/74, RUS 3/2013. 
</p>
<p> 81 See A/66/203, paras. 17-18, A/69/307, paras. 84-89.  
</p>
<p> 82 See also A/HRC/19/41, paras. 48-73. 
</p>
<p> 83 See CCPR/C/TUR/CO/1, para. 10, CEDAW/C/NOR/CO/8, paras. 33-34.  
</p>
<p> 84 See CCPR/C/JAM/CO/3, paras. 8- 9, A/HRC/14/20, paras. 20-23. See also UN Free &amp; Equal 
</p>
<p>factsheet, &#8220;Criminalization&#8221; (available at www.unfe.org/en/fact-sheets). 
</p>
<p> 85 See A/64/272, para. 46. 
